
## Observable Trends
1) Of the four drug variables observed in this exercise, only Capomulin hade any noticeable impact on reducing tumor mass.
2) However, none of the variables completely stopped the spread of metastatic sites.
3) In terms of surviving the treatments, Capomulin was clearly the safest choice, while Infubinol was actually more deadly than just using a placebo.

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

```


```python
clinical_trial_df = pd.read_csv("clinicaltrial_data.csv")
mouse_drug_df = pd.read_csv("mouse_drug_data.csv")

drop_mouse_id = clinical_trial_df.loc[clinical_trial_df.duplicated(subset=['Mouse ID', 'Timepoint']),'Mouse ID'].unique()

clean_clinical_df = clinical_trial_df[clinical_trial_df['Mouse ID'].isin(drop_mouse_id)==False]
clean_mouse_df = mouse_drug_df[mouse_drug_df['Mouse ID'].isin(drop_mouse_id)==False]

combined_data = pd.merge(clean_clinical_df, clean_mouse_df, on="Mouse ID")

combined_data.rename(columns={'Mouse ID':'Mouse', 'Tumor Volume (mm3)': 'Tumor Size'}, inplace=True)
combined_data.head()
```

```python
pct_changes = (tumor_pct_change['Capomulin'],
               tumor_pct_change['Infubinol'],
               tumor_pct_change['Ketapril'],
               tumor_pct_change['Placebo'])

fig, ax = plt.subplots()
ind=np.arange(len(pct_changes))
width=1
rectsPass=ax.bar(ind[0], pct_changes[0], width, color='green', ec='black')
rectsFail=ax.bar(ind[1:], pct_changes[1:], width, color='red', ec='black')

ax.set_ylabel('% Tumor Volume Change')
ax.set_title('Tumor Change Over 45 Day Treatment')
ax.set_xticks(ind)
ax.set_xticklabels(('Capomulin', 'Infubinol','Ketapril','Placebo'))
ax.set_autoscaley_on(False)
ax.set_ylim(-30,70)
ax.set_xlim(-0.5,3.5)

ax.grid(True)

def autolabelFail(rects):
    for rect in rects:
        height = rect.get_height()
        ax.text(rect.get_x()+rect.get_width()/2., 3,
                '%d%%' % int(height), 
                ha='center', va='bottom',color='white')
        
def autolabelPass(rects):
    for rect in rects:
        height = rect.get_height()
        ax.text(rect.get_x()+rect.get_width()/2., -8,
                '%d%%' % int(height), ha='center',
                va='bottom',color='white')
autolabelPass(rectsPass)
autolabelFail(rectsFail)
plt.savefig('Fig4.png')
plt.show()
```
